announcements.name: Patch Notes 0.20.1 - Chocolate Factory, Hoppity’s Hunt, and more!
announcements.description: Hello!  Welcome to Hypixel SkyBlock Patch 0.20.1. Today’s update has plenty of things in store, featuring Hoppity’s Hunt and Chocolate Factory, a follow-up patch for Glacite Tunnels, some long-awaited Dark Auction changes, and much more!  Read on to find out more about this release.

announcements.name: Quick Design Thread: Hunting and Attributes
announcements.description: Hello,  Today, I'd like to discuss "Hunting," a new skill to be introduced in the Foraging Update, and its relationship with Attributes.
